description:
This is a 31 minute workout called 'Overcome the Villain Voice Row' from the channel Aquil Abdullah.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Light.

Original workout description: Confront negative self-talk head-on in this powerful session with Aquil that focuses on self-compassion and inner strength. He guides you through three invigorating 10-minute climbs, ranging from 20 to 26 strokes per minute, helping you silence the villain's voice within.  Max rhythm: 26, Format: Climb...
